content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Oct 20 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar, on Monday, reaffirmed Pakistanas commitment to further deepening PakistanaEU cooperation, including under the GSP+ framework. The DPM/FM received and congratulated the newly appointed EU Ambassador to Pakistan Raimundas Karoblis,a Foreign Office Spokesperson said in a press release. Recent regional and international developments were also discussed during the meeting.
